Peter Dada, Akure TheÂ  All Progressives Congress in Ese Odo Local Government Area of Ondo State has reportedly expelled the lawmaker from the council area, Mr Success Torukerijoh. Torukerijoh is a member of the Ondo State House of Assembly representing Ese Odo state Constituency. He is one of the nine lawmakers opposing the impeachment of the state deputy governor, Mr Agboola Ajayi. He was said to have been expelled for involving in anti-party activities. The action was taken during the meeting of the leaders of the party in the local government on Sunday. Details soon